Experiment 1 Results (v1.3)

Feb 16, 2021

Feb 16 Update

  • Text box appears immediately, RT computed by time to begin typing
  • High/low memory words selected by concreteness in addition to recall probability
  • Exclusion threshold set to 25% accuracy

Exclusions

  • Excluding 4 participants who gave incorrect resonses on fewer than 25% of trials, leaving 26 participants in the analysis.
  • Dropping 65 trials with reaction times over more than 3 sds above the mean (more than 8.2 seconds), leaving 429 trials in the analysis.
